fields.name: Chess
fields.description: Chess is a strategic board game for two players where each commands an army of unique pieces on a checkered battlefield, maneuvering to capture the opponent's king.

fields.name: Monopoly
fields.description: Monopoly is a property trading board game where players buy, rent, and develop properties while trying to bankrupt their opponents.

fields.name: Scrabble
fields.description: Scrabble is a word game where players score points by placing letter tiles to form words on a board with premium squares.

fields.name: Jenga
fields.description: Jenga is a tension-filled dexterity game where players take turns removing blocks from a tower until it collapses.

fields.name: Uno
fields.description: Uno is a card-matching game where players race to empty their hands by playing cards that match the color or number of the top card.

fields.name: Connect Four
fields.description: Connect Four is a vertical strategy game where players drop colored discs into a grid, trying to align four in any direction.
